Class mst.Graph

  • java.lang.Object
    • mst.Graph
  • Enclosing class:
    mst

    private class mst.Graph
extends java.lang.Object
    The inner class Graph is used to generate a graph given number of vertex and density. Using this class to generate the graph, one can get a graph that not too much uniformity, say, the degree of a node can be varies a lot. See details in createGraph().
    Author:
    Da Zhao
